        "text": "Community contributor dan-and landed SearXNG + Firecrawl integration. Any model — including local Ollama — can now ground persona research with live web results. SearXNG searches, the default LLM synthesizes. Firecrawl scrapes JS-heavy pages for URL imports. Both opt-in, both fallback-safe. Settings UI has a \"Test search\" button. New docker-compose.ollama.yml for one-command local deployment."
      }
